---
title: "Home"
description: "Brian Anders is an Engineer Manager in the tech industry. I'm also a Youtuber, Podcaster, and Musician."
priority: 1.0
homepage: true
pageClasses:
  - 'main'
  - 'home'
layout: base
styles:
  - 'main'
scripts:
  - 'homepage'
---


<%- partial('head/styles', {...locals, path: 'homepage', inlineStyles: true, }) %>


<section class="intro">
  <div class="content">
    <header>
      <h2>
        <%- noWidows('Who am I?'); %>
      </h2>
    </header>
    <p>
      <%- noWidows(`I am Brian Anders, an Engineer Manager in the tech industry. My specialty is in building enterprise level e-commerce websites.`); %>
    </p>
    <p>
      <%- `I cohost a podcast and YouTube channel about Batman with my friend ${externalLink('Alex Cash', { href: 'https://alex.cash' })}, called ${externalLink('Bat Lessons', { href: locals.batLessons })}. I also record drum covers for my YouTube channel, ${link('Banders Drums', { href: locals.bandersDrums.youtube })}.` %>
    </p>
    <p>
      <%- noWidows(`I have a strong passion for music.  In my free time, I listen to a lot of music, play some other instruments, and try to keep up with a lot of different podcasts.`); %>
    </p>
    <p>
      <%- noWidows(`You can find me on the internet in some other places.`) %>
      <% const contactLinks = [
          { copy: 'Github',    href: locals.github,    },
          { copy: 'Instagram', href: locals.instagram, },
          { copy: 'Last.fm',   href: locals.lastfm,    },
          { copy: 'LinkedIn',  href: locals.linkedin,  },
          { copy: 'Mastodon',  href: locals.mastodon,  rel: 'me' },
          { copy: 'Twitter',   href: locals.twitter,   },
          { copy: 'YouTube',   href: locals.bandersDrums.youtube, },
        ].map(item => externalLink(item.copy, item));
      %>
      <%- contactLinks.join(', '); %>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="contributions">
  <div class="content">
    <h2><%- noWidows('Shows and other fun stuff'); %></h2>
    <div class="deck">
    <%
      const model = [
        {
          heading: "Podcast & Youtube channel: Bat Lessons",
          image: "/images/about/contributions/batlessons.webp",
          copyBlock: `My friend ${externalLink('Alex Cash', { href: 'https://alex.cash' })} and I cohost a show about Batman. It focuses on the context around the development of the characters, the history of the Batman universe, and the impact that our world had on it.`,
          links: [
            {
              label: "Bat Lessons website",
              url: locals.batLessons,
            }
          ]
        }, {
          heading: "YouTube channel: Banders Drums",
          image: "/images/drums/logo.png",
          copyBlock: "I have a YouTube channel where I post recordings of me playing drum covers. I plan to compose my own music someday.",
          links: [
            {
              label: "Main Web Page",
              path: locals.bandersDrums.path,
            }, {
              label: "YouTube Channel",
              url: locals.bandersDrums.youtube,
            }
          ]
        },
      ]
      model.forEach(({ copyBlock, image, heading, links }) => {
    %>
        <%- partial('contributions-card', Object.assign(locals, { copyBlock, image, heading, links })); %>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content center">
    <%- link('More about me', {
      href: '/about/',
      class: 'button mega-button',
    }); %>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="posts">
  <div class="content center">
    <header>
      <h2>
        <%- noWidows('Recent posts.'); %>
      </h2>
    </header>
    <%- partial('posts-list', Object.assign(locals, { postCount: 6 })); %>
    <%- link('More posts', {
      href: '/posts/',
      class: 'button mega-button',
    }); %>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="index-music">
  <div class="content">
    <header>
      <h2>
        <%- noWidows('What I have been listening to.'); %>
      </h2>
      <p>
        <%- noWidows('Music is a big deal to me. I am always looking for my next favorite album. Last.fm is a tool that I use to track my listening habits. Here is some of the music that Iâ€™ve been listening to recently.'); %>
      </p>
    </header>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://ws.audioscrobbler.com" crossorigin />
    <div class="last-fm-module p" data-type="albums" src="/images/posts/last-fm/default.webp">
      <% for (let i = 0; i < 4; i++) { %>
        <%- defaultLastFMModule(); %>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="center">
      <%- link('More music details', {
        href: '/posts/last-fm/',
        class: 'button mega-button',
      }); %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
